 Developers | first1 = Jack | last1 = Nicas | first2 = Kellen | last2 = Browning | date = 2021-09-10 | accessdate = 2021-09-10 | work = The New York Times | archive-date = 2021-09-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210912002720/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/09/10/technology/epic-apple-app-developers.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。Epic不服判决，向[[美国联邦第九巡回上诉法院|美国联邦第九巡回上诉法院]]上诉<ref>{{cite web | url = https://apnews.com/article/lifestyle-technology-lawsuits-san-francisco-apple-inc-52febb143da2907490e42f813f5f277f | title = Epic Games appeals ruling in lawsuit alleging Apple monopoly | first= Tom | last= Krisher | date = 2021-09-12 | accessdate = 2021-09-12 | publisher = Associated Press }}</ref>。

