苹果经常被指控采用[[计划报废|计划报废]]手段，增加新品销量<ref name="stiles">{{cite web|last1=Stiles|first1=Jackson|title=This is how long your Apple iPhone will last|url=http://thenewdaily.com.au/life/tech/2016/04/18/iphone-life-expectancy/|publisher=The New Daily|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Tsukayama|first1=Hayley|title=The problem with Apple’s war on this age-old design|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2016/08/08/the-problem-with-apples-war-on-this-age-old-design/|publisher=The Washington Post|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cracking the Apple Trap|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/03/magazine/why-apple-wants-to-bust-your-iphone.html|publisher=The New York Times Magazine|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Planned Obsolescence, as Myth or Reality|url=https://economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2013/10/31/planned-obsolescence-as-myth-or-reality/|publisher=The New York Times|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Jones|first1=Brad|title=PLANNED OBSOLESCENCE HAS LED TO RIDICULOUS PRODUCT CYCLES, AND IT’S TIME TO SAY ENOUGH IS ENOUGH|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/apple-iphone-7-planned-obsolescence/|publisher=Digital Trends|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref>。2015年12月，纽约州有民众集体起诉，指控[[iOS_9|iOS 9]]更新采用计划报废<ref>{{cite web|title=IOS 9 Slows iPhone 4S Complaint|url=https://www.scribd.com/document/294247024/IOS-9-Slows-iPhone-4S-Complaint|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Pelegrin|first1=Williams|title=Furious iPhone 4S owners sue Apple for $5M, alleging iOS 9 crippled their phones|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/mobile/iphone-4s-planned-obsolescence-lawsuit/|publisher=Digital Trends|accessdate=2016-08-30}}</ref>。消费者小组SumOfUs在2016年7月发出在线请愿书，指控苹果利用软件升级“破坏”设备，旨在拖慢老旧机型<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bogart|first1=Nicole|title=Is Apple guilty of using ‘planned obsolescence’ to force iPhone users into upgrading?|url=http://globalnews.ca/news/2926170/is-apple-guilty-of-using-planned-obsolescence-to-force-iphone-users-into-upgrading/|publisher=Global News|accessdate=2016-09-08}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=SomOfUs Petition: Apple: Don't push iOS "upgrades" which sabotage older iPhones and iPads|url=https://actions.sumofus.org/a/planned-obsolescence-is-why-apple-isn-t-a-green-company/|publisher=SumOfUs|accessdate=2016-09-08}}</ref>。2016年9月，该组织又发布请愿书，指责苹果计划在[[iPhone_7|iPhone 7]]中淘汰标准[[TRS端子|耳机插孔]]，征集到30万签名<ref>{{cite web|last1=Abbany|first1=Zulfikar|title=iPhone 7 petition: Apple 'screwing customers and planet' with headphone jack|url=http://www.dw.com/en/iphone-7-petition-apple-screwing-customers-and-planet-with-headphone-jack/a-18980996|accessdate=2016-09-08|publisher=Deutsche Welle}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Apple is ditching the standard headphone jack to screw consumers and the planet|url=https://actions.sumofus.org/a/iphone-headphone-jack|publisher=SumOfUs|accessdate=2016-09-08|archive-date=2016-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909082944/https://actions.sumofus.org/a/iphone-headphone-jack|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

