ogram |work=Tech Crunch |date=2013-06-06 |accessdate=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607163445/http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/06/google-facebook-apple-deny-participation-in-nsa-prism-program/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

